parameters:
I don't think that just repenting will make my
sins lighter... but I want to change and repent,
even if it's just a little...

Konoha-sama, you have become even more beautiful.
You really resemble Lisa-sama. I also want to be
blessed with such beauty.

This church really brings a sense of peace,
doesn't it?

Thank you for the improvement in the situation,
whether my prayers have been answered or not...

Oh Konoha, today I made your favorite stew. You
should start learning how to cook soon.

Mother, I was called by someone from the castle
earlier. I'm not sure about the details, but it
seems like something happened.

Well... I wonder what it is this time. I hope it
gets resolved quickly...

Yes, I can't imagine anything happening on such
peaceful days. Just to be safe, I'll go to the
castle and see what's going on.
